          }
        },
        "text_VWcEbq": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Whether your shopping for an engagement ring, wedding band or if you would just like to add a new ring to your jewellery box, getting the right size is essential for comfort and style. </p>"
