            "border_width": 1,
            "note_text": "EU sizes are based on inner circumference (mm) and Japan sizes follow the JIS numeric scale. As with all international conversions, these are close equivalents — if you're ordering from outside the UK, we recommend confirming with the millimetre diameter measurement for the most accurate fit.",
